# to do something that is not needed (''literally:'' to carry firewood into the woods); see [[bring owls to Athens]] and [[carry coals to Newcastle]]
#*''Дарить ей книгу, что в лес дрова возить.'' [http://www.rg-rb.de/ch&k/2006/158/12.shtml]
